Class GUIHandler

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
it.polimi.ingsw.View.GUI.GUIHandler
public class GUIHandler
extends javafx.application.Application
this class contains utilities to manage the GUI, and a reference to the elements that are shared among all the controllers of the GUI

      public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)

    • createNonCloseableWindow

      public static void createNonCloseableWindow​(ViewController controller, java.lang.String fxmlPath, int width, int length)
